t's time what I said in my rant is said, perhaps some good will come out of it. If there are any suicide attempts made after reading this rant, I will write an additional rant on how pathetic those attempts were. In other words Troy, if you read this, it's meant as constructive criticism and you shouldn't get your panties in a bunch over it.<br>
